description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 21, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 42, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Leverage for East, Stringalong for South, and 3 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40212-96732-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [42 Votes, Common]
